title: Rangers in playoffs, near AL West title after edging Angels
text:
> Texas Rangers in playoffs, near AL West title after edging Angels Texas Rangers' Shin-Soo Choo of South Korea points to Adrian Beltre standing on second after Beltre's bases clearing double in the fifth inning of a baseball game against the Los Angeles Angels Thursday, Oct. 1, 2015, in Arlington, Texas. Choo, Delino DeShields and Robinson Chirinos scored on the hit. (AP Photo/Tony Gutierrez)
